                        <div id="page-title">
                            研究员钟伟的人事档案
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/weizhong/personnel.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="personnel.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>认真的说，他只是长得太TM丑了。 -O5议会。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>姓名：</strong>钟伟（Wei Zhong）</p>
<p><strong>安保权限等级</strong> -1</p>
<p><strong>历史：</strong>[数据删除编辑（DATA EXPUNGIDACTED）]</p>
<p><strong>职务：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">没有人真正知道研究员钟伟到底是在这儿干什么的。这家伙他妈的是谁？</span></p>
<p>研究员钟伟是基金会一名<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">重要的</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">关键的</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">有价值的</span> 有高度价值的成员，他参与收容了以下SCP项目：</p>
<p><a href="/scp-1842">SCP-1842</a>: Dr. Wondertainment的魔法微波炉！</p>
<p><a href="/scp-1644">SCP-1644</a>: 方尖碑</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2006">SCP-2006</a>: 太吓人啦</p>
<p><a href="/scp-1758">SCP-1758</a>: 啊！我亲爱的爸爸</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2012">SCP-2012</a>: 军灵现世</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2050">SCP-2050</a>: 松鼠十字军</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2800">SCP-2800</a>: 仙人掌侠</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2440">SCP-2440</a>: The Sealed King</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2101">SCP-2101</a>: 始皇守陵军</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2201">SCP-2201</a>: 超时空理发店</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2950">SCP-2950</a>: 一把椅子</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2301">SCP-2301</a>: 屠魔歌</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2599">SCP-2599</a>: 不够好</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2750">SCP-2750</a>: 纳瓦霍皮行者</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2499">SCP-2499</a>: 天球和谐</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/scp-2625">SCP-2625</a>: Chipperee Mine</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2775">SCP-2775</a>: 仿冒仁类</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2925">SCP-2925</a>: 交易之球</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2588">SCP-2588</a>: The Collective Consciousness of Arthur H. Jones</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/scp-2896">SCP-2896</a>: To Sleep, Perchance to Dream (of Freedom)</p>
<p><a href="/scp-3200">SCP-3200</a>: 时因</p>
<hr />
<p>研究员钟伟也参与编写了以下<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">惊悚同人</span> 报告：</p>
<p><a href="/a-broken-tool">A Broken Tool</a>: 关于<a href="/scp-326">SCP-326</a>的一则故事</p>
<p><a href="/the-meaning-of-fear">The Meaning of Fear</a>: An alternate take on <a href="/scp-2006">SCP-2006</a></p>
<p><a href="/right">Right?</a>: A tale about D-Class personnel.</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/leisure-time">Leisure Time</a>: A tale about researchers and relaxation.</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/the-tinkerer">The Tinkerer</a>: A tale of origins and tinkering.</p>
<p><a href="/mainline-hub">Mainline Series</a></p>
<ol>
<li>第一章: <a href="/spirit-dust">Spirit Dust</a></li>
<li>第二章: <a class="newpage" href="/of-meetings-and-meals">Of Meetings and Meals</a></li>
<li>第三章: <a class="newpage" href="/trip-hammer">Trip Hammer</a></li>
<li>第四章: <a class="newpage" href="/all-work-and-no-play">All Work and No Play</a></li>
</ol>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/eulogies">Eulogies</a>: The hardest part about funerals.</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/the-space-soldier">The Space Soldier</a>: A tale about the universe's finest soldier.</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/after-the-end">After The End</a>: A tale about what happens when everything goes wrong.</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/another-day-on-the-job">Another Day On the Job</a>: A tale about doing what's necessary.</p>
<hr />
<p>就连研究员钟伟也不知道这些该算什么：</p>
<p><a href="/unusual-incidents-unit-hub">特异事故处中心页</a></p>
<ol>
<li><a href="/uiu-file-1933-001">UIU档案1933-001</a></li>
</ol>
<hr />
<p>研究员钟伟发现以下报告需要<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">被扔进垃圾桶</span>大规模更新以纠正过时的材料：</p>
<p><a href="/scp-675">SCP-675</a>: 透窗之影</p>
<hr />
<p>研究员钟伟<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">据说</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">完全</span>绝对是帮助查看和校对了以下报告：</p>
<p><a href="/scp-754">SCP-754</a>: 虚实攀藤</p>
<p><a href="/scp-696">SCP-696</a>: 深渊打字机</p>
<p><a href="/log-of-anomalous-items">异常项目记录</a>: 异常项目记录</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="/scp-828">SCP-828</a>:</span> 被删除/重写（把我的工作抹掉了）</p>
<p><a href="/scp-660">SCP-660</a>: 陶制子宫</p>
<p><a href="/scp-261">SCP-261</a>: 次元泛用售货机</p>
<p><a href="/scp-190">SCP-190</a>: 玩具箱</p>
<hr />
<p>研究员钟伟<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">TMD应该重写了</span>给以下报告/SCP提供了灵感：</p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/a-double-life">A Double Life</a></p>
<p><a href="/scp-2008">SCP-2008</a></p>
<p><a href="/goc-tale-sequence-diplomacy">&quot;Diplomacy&quot;</a></p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/being-cactusman">Being Cactusman</a></p>
<p><a class="newpage" href="/cactus-insurgent">Cactus Insurgent</a></p>
<p><a href="/the-playful-beast">The Playful Beast</a></p>
<hr />
<p>我在聊天室里被如下称呼过：</p>
<p>&quot;Weizhong&quot; &quot;Weiz&quot; &quot;Wei&quot; &quot;Weezing&quot; &quot;Motherfucker&quot; &quot;Weighing&quot; &quot;whyzhong&quot;</p>
